the value of age in years.

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:21.960
Which means in some years if
you get a little bit less dose,

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.820
you can get a
little bit more dose

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:25.410
and still be
considered safe or not

00:05:25.410 --> 00:05:28.680
have any appreciable
increased risk.

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:30.810
And while you're
working, you should never

00:05:30.810 --> 00:05:34.920
get more than about 50
millisieverts in a given year.

