00:08:58.910 --> 00:09:01.220
And that's a heftier dose.

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:03.900
But also, the lens of the eye
is not a very massive organ.

00:09:03.900 --> 00:09:07.820
So this would mean do not stick
remaining eye in neutron beam,

00:09:07.820 --> 00:09:09.730
right?

00:09:09.730 --> 00:09:11.240
Or you've seen that
sticker, do not

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:14.270
