00:30:10.520 --> 00:30:12.720
just divide by 100.

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:17.880
So a regular old
chest X-ray, 0.1--

00:30:17.880 --> 00:30:19.620
let's see, how does it go?

00:30:19.620 --> 00:30:23.070
100 rem in a sievert.

00:30:23.070 --> 00:30:27.610
Yeah, so about 0.1
millisieverts, or 1,000 banana

00:30:27.610 --> 00:30:28.300
equivalent dose.

00:30:28.300 --> 00:30:29.620
Not terrible.

00:30:29.620 --> 00:30:34.350
Which is why if we go
back to that chart of all

00:30:34.350 --> 00:30:36.420
those relative
risks, if you look

00:30:36.420 --> 00:30:39.510
