00:31:50.560 --> 00:31:53.140
of developing cancer
much later down the line

00:31:53.140 --> 00:31:55.572
when that cell that
gets mutated divides.

00:31:55.572 --> 00:31:58.030
But it's probably going to save
your life in the next hour,

00:31:58.030 --> 00:31:59.270
or the next day.

00:31:59.270 --> 00:32:01.550
So definitely worth it.

00:32:01.550 --> 00:32:03.930
Let's see, the worst--

00:32:03.930 --> 00:32:05.820
what's the worst
