00:42:59.040 --> 00:43:02.892
And then out of here come lots
and lots and lots of neutrons.

00:43:02.892 --> 00:43:04.350
Enough neutrons
that you still need

00:43:04.350 --> 00:43:05.640
hot cells to deal with things.

00:43:05.640 --> 00:43:07.630
They're still quite
