00:43:07.630 --> 00:43:08.970
But it's not a reactor.

00:43:08.970 --> 00:43:11.220
Other ways of making neutrons.

00:43:11.220 --> 00:43:13.470
Speaking of, has anybody
seen the pulsed fusion source

00:43:13.470 --> 00:43:18.240
that we have down
