We have a pulse
neutron source that you

00:43:20.880 --> 00:43:23.400
can come take a look at.

00:43:23.400 --> 00:43:26.133
It's an electrostatic
fusion pulsed machine.

00:43:26.133 --> 00:43:28.050
There's a whole bunch
of tritium and deuterium

00:43:28.050 --> 00:43:31.440
in this palladium sponge,
what happens to hold hydrogen

00:43:31.440 --> 00:43:33.450
and its isotopes very well.

00:43:33.450 --> 00:43:36.240
And with a very quick pulse,
